WEBVTT


00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.025
Breaking news! 

00:00:01.025 --> 00:00:02.840
The door opens for regularization

00:00:02.920 --> 00:00:04.720
massive number of foreigners in Spain.

00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:06.280
The congress of deputies

00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:08.800
has just approved the consideration

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:10.760
of the popular legislative initiative

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:13.480
in order to regularize hundreds of thousands of citizens.

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:15.440
foreigners who are in a situation

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:16.640
irregular in Spain

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:19.420
since before November 1, 

00:00:19.420 --> 00:00:19.960
2021.

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:22.640
This vote does not mean immediate regularization,

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:25.040
but the beginning of the parliamentary procedures

00:00:25.160 --> 00:00:25.720
previous

00:00:25.721 --> 00:00:28.081
so that this initiative can become law.

00:00:28.280 --> 00:00:29.600
In case you get ahead,

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:30.560
this regularization

00:00:30.680 --> 00:00:31.520
extraordinary

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:33.880
will be the most widely approved in Spain.

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:36.040
The objective of this initiative is to regularize

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:38.880
about 500,000 foreigners in an irregular situation

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:41.840
and has been backed by more than 600,000 signatures,

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:43.440
as well as for more than 900

00:00:43.640 --> 00:00:44.200
organizations

00:00:44.201 --> 00:00:46.841
and various institutions of relevant importance.

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:47.680
Undoubtedly,

00:00:47.681 --> 00:00:50.121
today is 1 Great day for foreigners in Spain

00:00:50.122 --> 00:00:50.881
and let's hope

00:00:50.882 --> 00:00:53.801
that the year 2024 will also be the year in its entirety.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:55.640
What do you think of this measure?

00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:56.885
If you have any questions, 

00:00:56.885 --> 00:00:58.076
please feel free to contact us. 

00:00:58.076 --> 00:00:58.560
And remember,

00:00:58.640 --> 00:00:59.920
follow us for more videos
